These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, chestnut
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is not to the right of the person who likes chestnut##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Color   | chestnut | purple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Birthday   | november | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, german
1. the thai is somewhere to the left of the german##5
2. the german is on the left or right of the thai##3
3. the thai is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality   | thai | german |

 #################################

 
